data.description: Welcome home! This beautiful LGI home is ready for you to fall in love with! From the open concept floor plan (great for entertaining) to the backyard with breathtaking views at sunset, there is so much to love! Home is right across the street from a park as well! Come by and see all the amazing features for yourself! New lights installed in both bathrooms and the living room! This home is also solar, just another reason to come see this house today!
